00:04:35.950 --> 00:04:37.190
Times 3 times 3 times
3 times--

00:04:37.190 --> 00:04:39.340
MATT PARKER: When you are mixing
this up, there's a

00:04:39.340 --> 00:04:41.190
number of different ways you
could have mixed this up

00:04:41.190 --> 00:04:43.150
