00:05:21.630 --> 00:05:23.300
This is the total number of
ways if I could take the

00:05:23.300 --> 00:05:25.460
pieces off and then put
them back on again.

00:05:25.460 --> 00:05:27.540
Now, how many ways is
that all together?

00:05:27.540 --> 00:05:30.420
It's a very large number,
so we work it out.

00:05:30.420 --> 00:05:33.860
3 to the power 5.

